## Bundled fonts

A curated set of open-source monospace typefaces is embedded in the binary
so they are always available regardless of what is installed on the host OS.
Each font family is distributed under its own open-source license.

See `assets/fonts/THIRD-PARTY-FONTS.md` for the complete list of families,
SPDX license identifiers, and upstream URLs.

The full text of each individual license is present in the corresponding
font subdirectory under `assets/fonts/<family>/`.
